{"tid":1781460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"13 歲女燒國旗　被判12個月感化　官：不能因年輕就「乜都輕判」","createTime":"2019-12-13T07:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T10:45:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"080a5e6bd4d586fa411b30c17afbc7ab05aa3be4","tid":1781460,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"13 歲女童於 9 月 21 日的「光復屯門公園」遊行期間，焚燒屯門大會堂外的國旗，早前承認一項侮辱國旗罪，今（13日）在屯門裁判法院少年庭被判12個月感化令。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">裁判官水佳麗</span></strong>在判刑時指出，女童的感化官報告正面，事實上，女童亦非她想像中的「狂妄之徒」。鑑於社會事件仍未見結束的跡像，故水官特意提醒女童，沖昏頭腦、受人影響，「人哋叫做乜，你又做乜」是「好危險」，又指衝動、做事不考慮後果，是一件傻事，女童應該知道不少人因此失去自由，故提醒她須控制自己，三思而行。<br />\n<br />\n水官又指，法庭不能因為被告年輕就「乜都輕判」，強調法庭有其職責。女童被控於本年 9 月 21 日在屯門大會堂外，和其他兩名不知名人士，公開和故意以焚燒方式侮辱國旗。"},{"pid":"586c29d23f96c4eaffb30703522d2f83868b5c4e","tid":1781460,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"水菜麗"},{"pid":"0ea24ef2c2aca13c64e7205f60a0317171be659c","tid":1781460,"uid":124180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:26:55.000Z","msg":"屌你死黑警又揀官<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警二代性侵強姦：因年輕一時衝動-&gt;輕判感化<br />\n警多次偷竊：工作表現良好-&gt;輕判<br />\n三警涉插贓嫁禍：警告了事<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7b3169089419b22ff32244a47f7532b91c71fa","tid":1781460,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:27:37.000Z","msg":"有險可守"},{"pid":"ba71e2e6b246d1945a517e02bd35ae94b00c9e43","tid":1781460,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:32:03.000Z","msg":"死狗官我屌你老母"},{"pid":"998657c0a2319683f44c1b9c5787f2fc94e64ed2","tid":1781460,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:34:06.000Z","msg":"嘥氣，如果重判可以阻嚇到，一早冇人出黎示威"},{"pid":"d2f295185ed12aef276dba77189f5b04c3202989","tid":1781460,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T08:38:20.000Z","msg":"黑警先可以輕判，酷刑變傷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24b1f59273817ecad3780320436d84591969fcd","tid":1781460,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:29:52.000Z","msg":"包致金 姪女 呢？"},{"pid":"bcd49d4c527448729c291bcc99c0065c07bc3505","tid":1781460,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:31:58.000Z","msg":"正一閪官"},{"pid":"181ebdd66b71f73552046dcdb4bd3ab92af5e154","tid":1781460,"uid":51612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:32:53.000Z","msg":"狗官<br />\n<br />\n差佬非禮偷野就輕判無事"},{"pid":"b53c92b64a67de6d27f785bceedb62e494a4c7c8","tid":1781460,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:43:17.000Z","msg":"裁判官水佳麗認為本案案情不輕，她直斥少女「侮辱咗國家、貶損咗國家」，行為不能接受，因國旗關乎民族自尊，即使對中國無感情，但「中國人不燒中國旗，係最起碼嘅尊重」。"},{"pid":"bc513e24c1bc996396445b0a5d08d8d3bf7199f2","tid":1781460,"uid":301915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"感化係米入女童院?"},{"pid":"e45f2d37b12d65fdab155fbdbd5050bbeb22c60b","tid":1781460,"uid":23169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}